<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Makefile on cdeclog</title><link>https://cdecl.github.io/tags/makefile/</link><description>Recent content in Makefile on cdeclog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.154.5</generator><language>ko-kr</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 00:00:00 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://cdecl.github.io/tags/makefile/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Makefile Simple Template</title><link>https://cdecl.github.io/dev/makefile-simple-template/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://cdecl.github.io/dev/makefile-simple-template/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Makefile 간단한 범용 버전&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="makefile"&gt;Makefile&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;현재 디렉토리 모든 .cpp 파일 빌드&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-makefile" data-lang="makefile"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;CC&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; g++
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;CC_FLAGS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; -std&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;c++11 -pedantic -Wall -O2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;LD_LIBS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;EXEC&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; main
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;SOURCES&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;wildcard *.cpp&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;OBJECTS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;SOURCES:.cpp&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;.o&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#6272a4"&gt;# Main target
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#50fa7b"&gt;$(EXEC)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;OBJECTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;CC&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;OBJECTS&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; -o &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;EXEC&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;LD_LIBS&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#50fa7b"&gt;%.o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; %.cpp
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;CC&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; -c &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;CC_FLAGS&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; $&amp;lt; -o &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic"&gt;$@&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#50fa7b"&gt;clean&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; rm -f &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;EXEC&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;OBJECTS&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>